name: account
description: A read-only attribute that contains information about the user's account

subAttributes.name: canAuthenticate
subAttributes.description: A read-only attribute that specifies whether the user can authenticate at this time.

subAttributes.name: status
subAttributes.description: A read-only attribute that specifies the status of the account.

subAttributes.name: lockedAt
subAttributes.description: A read-only attribute that specifies the time at which the account was locked, if any.

subAttributes.name: secondsUntilUnlock
subAttributes.description: A read-only attribute that specifies the number of seconds remaining until the account will be unlocked.

subAttributes.name: unlockAt
subAttributes.description: A read-only attribute that specifies the time at which the account will be unlocked.
